title: Adobe Indesign CC (Cloud Installer) + License File
description:
HOW TO

1. Start "CreativeCloudSet-Up.exe" to launch the adobe installer.
2. create a free adobe ID or login to an existing one.
3. Install Indesign CC.
4. After install is complete, copy "amtlib.dll" into the installation folder.

Enjoy your free copy of Adobe Indesign CC!
